description: Tokio Marine Holdings, Inc. engages in non-life and life insurance, and financial and general businesses worldwide. It operates through four segments: Domestic Non-Life Insurance, Domestic Life Insurance, International Insurance, and Financial and Other. The company offers fire and allied lines, hull and cargo, health, personal accident, automobile, and other insurance products, as well as asset management services. It also provides investment advisory, investment trust, staffing, facility management, and nursing care services. The company was formerly known as Millea Holdings, Inc. and changed its name to Tokio Marine Holdings, Inc. in 2008. Tokio Marine Holdings, Inc. was incorporated in 2002 and is headquartered in Tokyo, Japan.
